  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Item
    This Interface has the basic methods that involve the product information.

    This Interface has the basic controls that all multimedia devices share.
    ScreenSpec
    This Interface declares the methods needed to obtain the screen specifications.

    AudioPlayer

    Controller
    This class handles all the events that user creates from the GUI.
    Employee

    Main
    This program sets up a basic GUI and connects to a data base that allows users to add products to the database.
